OL,4,Canniversary of Glasgow bin lorry crash
OL,6,FA former bishop who helped in the
OL,7,Faftermath of a bin lorry crash which
OL,8,Fclaimed six lives has said he will be
OL,9,Fpraying for the victims on the 10th
OL,10,Fanniversary of the tragedy.
OL,12,FThe incident on December 22, 2014 saw
OL,13,Fa 26-tonne Glasgow City Council refuse
OL,14,Ftruck veer out of control and crash
OL,15,Finto shoppers in the city centre.
OL,17,FIt travelled along the pavement in
OL,18,FQueen Street before crashing into the
OL,19,Fside of the Millennium Hotel in George
OL,20,FSquare.
