OL,6,FThe lorry was driven by Harry Clarke,
OL,7,Fnow aged 67, who has since said he
OL,8,Fthinks about the incident every day.
OL,10,FWitnesses saw Mr Clarke, who had
OL,11,Ffailed to disclose a previous blackout
OL,12,Fto his employers and the DVLA, slumped
OL,13,Fbehind the wheel.
