OL,6,FRight Rev Dr Gregor Duncan, the
OL,7,FScottish Episcopal Bishop of Glasgow
OL,8,Fand Galloway, was at the scene in the
OL,9,Faftermath of the crash.
OL,11,FHe told a memorial service at Glasgow
OL,12,FCathedral in 2015: "God is to be found
OL,13,Fin those who ran to help, in the
OL,14,Femergency services... in every tear
OL,15,Fshed."
OL,17,FMr Duncan, who retired in 2018, said
OL,18,Fhe will be praying for the victims on
OL,19,Fthe 10th anniversary on Sunday, and he
OL,20,Fadded he has also prayed for Mr Clarke.
