OL,6,FThe crash came just over a year after
OL,7,Fa helicopter crashed into the Clutha
OL,8,Fpub in Glasgow on November 29 2013,
OL,9,Fwith the loss of 10 lives.
OL,11,FRecalling the day of the bin lorry
OL,12,Fincident, Mr Duncan said: "That
OL,13,Fafternoon I went out, and when I went
OL,14,Fback the road was closed off with lots
OL,15,Fof people around. I saw human remains
OL,16,Fon the road, some covered, some not. I
OL,17,Frealised something terrible had
OL,18,Fhappened and went back to my office
OL,19,Fand put my clerical dress on.
