OL,6,F"Someone said to me out of the crowd
OL,7,F'Five souls, Father' ` by which she
OL,8,Fmeant five people had been killed, at
OL,9,Fthat stage, I didn't know how. She
OL,10,Fmight have been asking me to pray for
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"It happened soon after the Clutha and
OL,14,Fthe city felt stricken ` I think it
OL,15,Ffelt afflicted. The time of year made
OL,16,Fit even worse. Some tragedies happen
OL,17,Fout of thin air, but others happen
OL,18,Fbecause of human error or human folly."
