OL,6,FA mass was held at St Andrew's
OL,7,FCathedral in Glasgow soon after the
OL,8,Fincident, at which Archbishop Philip
OL,9,FTartaglia, who died in 2021, said
OL,10,FGlasgow had been "eagerly and
OL,11,Fcheerfully preparing for Christmas"
OL,12,Fwhen it was suddenly turned into "a
OL,13,Fcity of sadness and mourning".
OL,15,FA fatal accident inquiry held in 2015
OL,16,Ffound Mr Clarke lost consciousness at
OL,17,Fthe wheel before the crash.
