OL,6,FIt found the accident might have been
OL,7,Favoided if Mr Clarke had told the
OL,8,Ftruth about his medical history, after
OL,9,Fit emerged he had previously blacked
OL,10,Fout while at the wheel of a stationary
OL,11,Fbus.
OL,13,FThen lord advocate Frank Mulholland
OL,14,Fmade the decision not to prosecute Mr
OL,15,FClarke in 2016, and said he knew it
OL,16,Fwas "not a popular one".
OL,18,FThe Crown Office insisted there was
OL,19,Finsufficient evidence to raise
OL,20,Fcriminal proceedings.
