OL,6,FIn 2019, Mr Clarke told the Mail On
OL,7,FSunday the tragedy was an "accident"
OL,8,Fand said he was "devastated at what
OL,9,Fhappened".
OL,11,FMr Clarke said: "It has been made out
OL,12,Fthat I don't care about what happened.
OL,13,FThere's not a day goes by I don't
OL,14,Fthink about it."
OL,16,FIn 2021, Glasgow City Council took
OL,17,Flegal action against his former
OL,18,Femployer, First Bus, over the issue of
OL,19,Fjob references, but the bid failed.
